data.description: **OPEN HOUSE Sunday 12:00-2:00!**Corner unit in a convenient low-maintenance community! Open floor plan features the primary bedroom on the main floor with spacious en-suite bath. Eat-in kitchen island with additional dining area. Large living room and laundry room all on the first floor. Easy access into the kitchen from the 2-car attached garage. Upstairs features two additional bedrooms, a large full bathroom, and loft space (great for an office, or playroom). The home is part of Welden Village which offers a pool, playground, dog park, clubhouse, and walking trails for the community.
